content.p: This page contains a record of the University's incoming Quality Manual policies (and amendments to current policies). Its content is primarily directed at staff but may also be of interest to students across all of the UK, China and Malaysia campuses. Amendments to the Quality Manual for the 2024/25 academic session can be found on the following page: Recent Changes Student Services Academic-Service-Office@nottingham.edu.cn student_registry@nottingham.edu.my Quality-Manual-Enquiries@nottingham.ac.uk Portland Building, University of Nottingham University Park Nottingham, NG7 2RD
